              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Liquid He-3. The scattering volume is 50 mm high and",
                "  46 mm in diameter.",
                " In order to prevent tritium loss from the target and",
                " enclosed contamination of the beam line, the target",
                " was in a 0.5 bar helium atmosphere by a",
                "                           12 p.m molybdenum foil."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detectors were cylinders with a diameter of",
                "10 cm filled with NE 213. Six cylinders with a length",
                "of 20 cm were used with their axes in the vertical",
                "direction, and two short cylinders with a length of",
                "7.6 cm were oriented horizontally."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
